  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个微支付系统的架构图，核心是µpay这个智能合约模块。它负责处理服务扣费和用户账户管理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "µpay",
        "smart contract"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，µpay作为核心合约。那用户和服务是怎么跟它交互的？我看到有User0、User1这些，还有Service0到Service3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User0",
        "User1",
        "Service0",
        "Service1",
        "Service2",
        "Service3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，User0和Service0是扣费的发起方。User0代表Redis缓存服务，Service0是IngressController，它们通过dt=-0.1和dt=+0.1的时间差参数跟µpay交互，模拟异步扣费确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User0",
        "Service0",
        "µpay",
        "dt = -0.1",
        "dt = +0.1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，User0用RedisCache，Service0用IngressController，双向虚线连接µpay。那User1和Service1呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User0",
        "Service0",
        "µpay",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "User1也是RedisCache，但它和Service1的LoadBalancer是从µpay接收扣费结果的一方，所以箭头方向反过来，µpay指向它们。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User1",
        "Service1",
        "µpay",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加µpay到User1和Service1的出边。这些都在service smart contract子图里对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "µpay",
        "User1",
        "Service1",
        "service smart contract"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。现在需要另一个子图叫withdrawal，处理提现流程。核心是tx3节点，用WorkerNode实现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "withdrawal",
        "tx3",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "withdrawal子图，tx3作为WorkerNode。那哪些节点参与提现？User1和Service1会连过来吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "withdrawal",
        "tx3",
        "User1",
        "Service1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，User1在这里换成LoadBalancer角色，Service1换成IngressController，它们都虚线连到tx3。另外tx3还要输出到User2、Service2、Service3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User1",
