      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有样式已应用。我注意到User1在两个子图里用了不同的基础设施类型，smart contract里是RedisCache，withdrawal里是LoadBalancer，这样设计是有意的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
